14:
From the descendants of Levi who returned to Judah there was: Shemaiah son of Hasshub;
\li2 Hasshub son of Azrikam;
\li2 Azrikam son of Hashabiah;
\li2 Hashabiah was a descendant of Levi's youngest son Merari.
